:absolute;border:0;" allowfullscreen scrolling="no" data-embed-domain="www.youtube.com"></iframe></div><p>在<em>《忍者神龟传说》中，</em>兄弟俩发现自己面对的是反派毕肖普（现在被描绘成一名女性），该系列的长期粉丝应该对毕肖普很熟悉。被毕肖普分开后，他们将不得不独自站立，直到找到彼此并再次并肩作战。该剧共 12 集，将在 Paramount+ 独家播出。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/the-new-2d-animated-teenage-mutant-ninja-turtles-show-hits-paramount-on-august-9-163555708.html?src =rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/the-new-2d-animated-teenage-mutant-ninja-turtles-show-hits-paramount-on-august-9-163555708.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> f8de96d8-d6f9-4151-ac9a-0ab212aee3a2 </guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Cheyenne MacDonald]]></dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Sun, 09 Jun 2024 16:35:55 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1717950996</ingested><modified> 2024-06-09T16:36:40+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Cheyenne MacDonald]]></category><media:content height="818" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-06%2Fca10c980-267d-11ef-8fff-a899c68df1a2&amp;resize=1400%2C818&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=cea965a8984bfcfe3531e358c10b8d9193dfffef" width="1400"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="818" medium="image" 